  "text": "Input: Words: W, Number of topics: K, Topic penalty: λ, Topics: ψ for every document j do Let f i = λ for all topics i. Initialize all word tokens to be unmarked. while there are unmarked tokens do Pick the topic i and set of unmarked tokens T that minimizes [CITATION_1] . Let f i = 0 and mark all tokens in T . Assign z jt = i for all t ∈ T . end while end for Output: Assignments Z.",
